OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with prolonged evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry with long clear
OL,8,Fspells and turning chilly, with a
OL,9,Ftouch of ground frost in sheltered
OL,10,Fspots. Winds mostly light but becoming
OL,11,Fbreezier along the coast and over
OL,12,Fhills.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry and fine, with long sunny
OL,15,Fspells. Warm or very warm inland but a
OL,16,Fbrisk breeze, especially around
OL,17,Fcoasts, giving a noticeably cooler
OL,18,Ffeel here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
