OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, dry and very warm with
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Lighter winds. Thursday,
OL,8,Fcooler and breezy with sunshine and
OL,9,Fshowers. Friday, mostly dry but
OL,10,Fgenerally cloudier with occasional
OL,11,Fbright spells. Breezier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
